on powers of 2. Specifically, each term appears to be formed by adding a \
doubling sequence to the previous term.\\n\\nThus, the general formula for \
the nth term can be identified as:\\n- \\\\( a_n = a_{n-1} + 2^{n+1} \\\\)\\n\
