a=1, b=-5, c=1\n    print(\"Roots are reciprocal:\", result)\nexcept \
ValueError as e:\n    print(e)\n```\n\nThis function takes the coefficients \
\\( a \\), \\( b \\), and \\( c \\) of the quadratic equation and returns \
`True` if the roots are reciprocal and `False` otherwise. It also checks if \
\\( a \\) is non-zero to ensure a valid quadratic equation."}}, 
