             "Here is a Python function that checks whether a sequence of \
numbers has a decreasing trend:\n\n```python\ndef \
has_decreasing_trend(sequence):\n    if len(sequence) < 2:\n        return \
False  # Not enough elements to determine a trend\n    return all(sequence[i] \
> sequence[i + 1] for i in range(len(sequence) - 1))\n\n# Example usage:\n\
