converting the `large` array into a set (`large_set`), you can leverage the \
average O(1) time complexity for membership checks in a set.\n2. **Iterate \
Over the Small Array**: For each element in the `small` array, check if it \
exists in the `large_set`.\n3. **Return the Result**: If any element in \
