\\n### Explanation:\\n1. **Function Definition**: The function \
`is_tuple_valid` takes a tuple `tup` as an argument.\\n2. **Iteration**: It \
iterates over each item in the tuple.\\n3. **Validation Check**: For each \
item, it checks:\\n   - If the item is an instance of `int`.\\n   - If the \
