Count the number of distinct powers.\n\nHere's a Python function to achieve \
this:\n\n```python\ndef count_distinct_prime_powers(n):\n    def \
prime_factors(n):\n        i = 2\n        factors = {}\n        while i * i \
<= n:\n            while (n % i) == 0:\n                if i in factors:\n    \
                factors[i] += 1\n                else:\n                    \
factors[i] = 1\n                n //= i\n            i += 1\n        if n > \
