in pairs. Here's a function that accomplishes this:\\n\\n```python\\ndef \
tuple_to_dict(tup):\\n    # Check if the tuple has an even number of elements\
\\n    if len(tup) % 2 != 0:\\n        raise ValueError(\\\"Tuple must \
contain an even number of elements.\\\")\\n\\n    # Create a dictionary using \
