Not balanced\n        # Ignore all other characters\n    \n    # If the stack \
is empty, all opening brackets were matched correctly\n    return not stack\n\
\n# Example usage:\nexpression = \"{[()()]}\"\nprint(is_balanced(expression)) \
 # Output: True\n\nexpression = \"{[(])}\"\nprint(is_balanced(expression))  # \
Output: False\n```\n\n### Explanation:\n1. **Stack Initialization**: The \
