Python:\\n\\n```python\\ndef count_chars_with_vowel_neighbors(s):\\n    \
vowels = set('aeiouAEIOU')\\n    count = 0\\n    n = len(s)\\n    \\n    for \
i in range(1, n - 1):\\n        # Check if the character has vowels as both \
neighbors\\n        if s[i-1] in vowels and s[i+1] in vowels:\\n            \
