combination, calculate the sum.\n\n3. **Store Unique Sums**: Use a set to \
store the sums to ensure they are unique.\n\nHere's how the code would look:\n\
\n```python\nfrom itertools import product\n\ndef \
find_combinations_of_sums(tuple_list):\n    # Use itertools.product to find \
