\"\"\"\n    Find the n cheapest price items from a given dataset using a heap \
queue algorithm.\n\n    Parameters:\n    items (list of tuples): A list where \
each tuple contains the item name and its price, e.g., [(\"item1\", 10), \
(\"item2\", 5)].\n    n (int): The number of cheapest items to find.\n\n    \
