return cheapest_items\n\n# Example usage:\nitems = [(\"item1\", 10), (\"item2\
\", 5), (\"item3\", 20), (\"item4\", 3), (\"item5\", 15)]\nn = 3\n\
print(find_n_cheapest_items(items, n))\n```\n\n### Explanation:\n- \
