remove_whitespaces(input_string)\\nprint(result)  # Output: \
\\\"Hello,howareyou?\\\"\\n```\\n\\n### Explanation:\\n- The `split()` \
method, when called without any arguments, splits the string at all \
whitespace and returns a list of the words.\\n- `''.join()` then concatenates \
these words back together without any spaces, effectively removing all \
whitespace.\""}}, 
