(3, 4), (5, 6)]\nlist_b = [(1, 2), (3, 4), (5, 6)]\nlist_c = [(1, 2), (3, 5), \
(5, 6)]\n\nprint(are_lists_identical(list_a, list_b))  # Output: True\n\
print(are_lists_identical(list_a, list_c))  # Output: False\n```\n\n### \
