element appears in the array.\n2. **Pair Calculation**: For each element with \
a frequency greater than 1, the number of pairs that can be formed is \
calculated using the formula for combinations: \\( \\text{count} \\times \
(\\text{count} - 1) / 2 \\).\n3. **Summing Up Pairs**: Sum these calculated \
