             Style["Response:", Bold], 
             "To find the sum of the first even and the first odd number in a \
given list, you can follow these steps in a Python function:\n\n```python\n\
def sum_of_first_even_and_odd(numbers):\n    first_even = None\n    first_odd \
= None\n\n    for num in numbers:\n        if first_even is None and num % 2 \
