Python function to check if two strings are isomorphic:\\n\\n```python\\ndef \
are_isomorphic(s, t):\\n    if len(s) != len(t):\\n        return False\\n\\n \
   # Create two dictionaries to store the mappings of characters\\n    s_to_t \
