Explanation:\n1. **Base Case**: If both elements are numbers (integers or \
floats), directly subtract them.\n2. **Recursive Case**: If both elements are \
tuples, ensure they have the same length, then recursively subtract each \
corresponding element.\n3. **Error Handling**: Raise a `ValueError` if the \
