`right`:\n   - If the element at `left` is smaller or equal to the element at \
`right`, try to append `arr[left]` to `sorted_array` if it maintains the \
sorted order.\n   - Otherwise, try to append `arr[right]`.\n3. **Check Sorted \
Order**: At each step, ensure that appending the chosen element maintains the \
sorted order of `sorted_array`.\n4. **Return Result**: If you can construct \
the sorted array using this method, return `True`; otherwise, return \
`False`."}}, Alignment -> {Left, Top}], {400, Automatic}], "Tooltip"]& ], 
