the rest to have 6 beads in each part:\\n\\nLet \\\\( x \\\\) be the number \
of beads removed from each part. After removing \\\\( x \\\\) beads, the \
remaining beads are doubled to give 6 beads:\\n\\n\\\\[ 2(13 - x) = 6 \
