during the season.  The old record was 300 points during the season.  How \
many points did James beat the old record by?\""}, {
              StyleBox["\"Response:\"", Bold, StripOnInput -> False], 
              "\"To find out how many points James scored in the season, we \
calculate his points from touchdowns and 2-point conversions.\\n\\n1. \
**Touchdown Points:**\\n   - James scores 4 touchdowns per game.\\n   - Each \
touchdown is worth 6 points.\\n   - There are 15 games in the season.\\n\\n   \
\\\\[\\n   \\\\text{Total touchdowns} = 4 \\\\times 15 = 60\\n   \\\\]\\n   \
\\\\[\\n   \\\\text{Points from touchdowns} = 60 \\\\times 6 = 360\\n   \\\\]\
\\n\\n2. **2-Point Conversion Points:**\\n   - James scores 2-point \
