130 minutes.\\n\\n3. **Calculate the total driving time:**\\n   - Total \
driving time = 110 minutes (to destination) + 130 minutes (back) = 240 \
minutes.\\n\\n4. **Convert the total driving time to hours:**\\n   - 240 \
