turtle} - \\\\text{Time for hare} = 20 \\\\text{ seconds} - 2 \\\\text{ \
seconds} = 18 \\\\text{ seconds}\\n\\\\]\\n\\nThus, the turtle needs an \
18-second head start.\\n\\n**Final Answer: 18 seconds**\""}}, 
