the time on uphill slopes, and one-third of the time on downhill slopes, what \
is his average speed in miles per hour?\""}, {
              StyleBox["\"Response:\"", Bold, StripOnInput -> False], 
              
              "\"To find Conner's average speed, we need to determine the \
