terms:\\n     \\\\[\\n     v_{\\\\text{avg}} = 20 + 24 + 14 = 58\\n     \\\\]\
\\n\\nTherefore, Conner's average speed is \\\\( \\\\boxed{58} \\\\) miles \
per hour.\""}}, 
