dividing both sides by 15:\\n\\n\\\\[\\nx = \\\\frac{450}{15} = 30\\n\\\\]\\n\
\\nThus, Missy put \\\\(\\\\$30\\\\) in the bank the first year. The final \
answer is:\\n\\n\\\\[\\n\\\\boxed{30}\\n\\\\]\""}}, 
