adults)} + 7 \\\\, \\\\text{(eggs for girls)} + 2b \\\\, \\\\text{(eggs for \
boys)} = 36\\n\\\\]\\n\\nSimplifying the equation, we have:\\n\\n\\\\[\\n9 + \
