weight of Karen\[CloseCurlyQuote]s tote. Kevin\[CloseCurlyQuote]s work papers \
are a sixth of the weight of the contents of his full briefcase. If Karen\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]s tote weighs 8 pounds, how many more pounds does Kevin\
