\\\\)\\n2. Arnold's purchase: \\\\( a + b = 5 \\\\)\\n\\nWe need to find the \
value of \\\\( b \\\\). We can do this by solving the system of equations.\\n\
\\nFirst, solve the second equation for \\\\( a \\\\):\\n\\n\\\\[ a = 5 - b \
\\\\]\\n\\nSubstitute \\\\( a = 5 - b \\\\) into the first \
