\\\\]\\n\\nSubtract 10 from both sides:\\n\\n\\\\[ -b = 7 - 10 \
\\\\]\\n\\n\\\\[ -b = -3 \\\\]\\n\\nMultiply both sides by -1:\\n\\n\\\\[ b = \
