three people (Sally, Jenny, and Moses), the total entrance fee is:\\n\\\\[ 3 \
\\\\times 4 = 12 \\\\text{ dollars} \\\\]\\n\\nThe total amount they paid for \
their harvest is $128. Since the entrance fee is already deducted from this \
amount, we add back the entrance fees to find the original cost of the \
strawberries:\\n\\\\[ 128 + 12 = 140 \\\\text{ dollars} \\\\]\\n\\nThe price \
of strawberries is $20 per pound. Therefore, the number of pounds of \
