days.\n   - Therefore, the total consumption over these 122 days is \\( 122 \
\\, \\text{days} \\times 27 \\, \\text{bales/day} = 3294 \\) bales.\n\n3. \
**Calculate the Remaining Bales of Hay:**\n   - Start with 1344 bales from \
